No. 09-9000. Henry W. Skinner, Petitioner v. Lynn Switzer, District Attorney for the 31st Judicial District of Texas. 561 U.S. 1057, 131 S. Ct. 64,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1150,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5744. September 28, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for appointment of counsel granted. Robert C. Owen, Esquire, of Austin, Texas, is appointed to serve as counsel for the petitioner in this case.
